<div class="hero">
    <h1>BYA Unsupported Web App</h1>
    <p>This application intentionally uses technologies that <strong>Microsoft Azure does not support</strong>:</p>
    <ul class="tech-list">
        <li>
            <strong>.NET Core 2.1</strong> &mdash; End-of-life runtime. Azure App Service only supports
            current and LTS .NET releases; .NET Core 2.1 is no longer listed as a supported stack.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Amazon DynamoDB</strong> &mdash; AWS-native NoSQL database service. Azure has no
            native integration or managed offering for DynamoDB.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <a class="btn" asp-controller="Items" asp-action="Index">Browse Items &rarr;</a>
</div>
